synopsis.value: After KITH'RAK VOSS flees into the creche and ALANA SILVERSHIELD/Silvershield's replacement flies off, THE BUTCHER and his cohort remain: Several Death's Heads and a hobgoblin called RUUK who serves as his right hand. As you near him, THE BUTCHER slides his blood covered fingers down his mask, then speaks. His voice is low and monotone, the embodiment of quiet evil.
